      "id": "mem_062",
      "sourceId": "qmd_7863",
      "source": "qmd",
      "text": "[Vault/Research] Research: ESPN Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week, formatted as: # Research: ESPN Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week, formatted as  ## Summary This week's NCAA Division 1 men's lacrosse schedule features several key matchups across ESPN networks, primarily on Saturday, March 28th. Top-ranked teams like Notre Dame, Harvard, Syracuse, and North Carolina are scheduled to play. Most games will be available for streaming on ESPN+, with select high-profile games airing o",
