      "text": "[Vault/Research] Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week: # Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week  ## Summary Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week primarily feature the NCAA Championship matches scheduled for Memorial Day weekend, specifically May 23-25, 2026, with semifinals on Saturday and the final on Monday [1, 2]. Some individual games were also listed for Wednesday, March 25, on ESPN+ [3]. Most Division 1 games are broadcast on ESPN+ and FloLive [3, 10].  ## ",
