      "text": "[Vault/Research] Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week from ESPN, formatt: # Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week from ESPN, formatt  ## Summary A comprehensive review of ESPN's \"Live & Upcoming\" schedule reveals a significant number of NCAA Division 1 men's lacrosse games scheduled for this week, primarily on Saturday, with additional games on Tuesday and Friday. These matchups will be broadcast across various ESPN platforms including ESPNU, ACC Network (ACCN), ACCN",
