      "sourceId": "qmd_15501",
      "source": "qmd",
      "text": "House hunting requirements for a 65-year-old woman: - Budget for house: $400,000 (after taxes and retirement savings) - Location preference: Suburbs immediately outside Philadelphia, PA (Broomall, Upper Darby, Havertown) - Yard: Small, ideally fenced, for a dog - Square footage: 900-2000 sq ft - Property taxes: Below $8,000 per year",
