      "text": "[Vault/Research] Research: test: # Research: test  ## Research Report: Understanding Tests  ## Summary Tests serve as crucial evaluation tools across various domains, primarily in education and software development, to assess knowledge, skills, and system functionality. They encompass diverse types, from objective multiple-choice questions to in-depth subjective essays and specialized functional software evaluations. While offering significant benefits like improved learning retention and defect",
