      "text": "[Vault/Research] Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week from ESPN, formatt: # Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week from ESPN, formatt  ## Summary This week, NCAA Division I men's lacrosse features a robust schedule of games broadcast across ESPN platforms, including ESPN+, ESPNU, ACCN, and ACCNX. Key matchups include #5 Syracuse facing #4 North Carolina, #2 Richmond against #1 Notre Dame, and #10 Penn State battling #11 Johns Hopkins. Most games are available via ESPN",
